title: 2020 With Posh People | StreetSmart
description: In this video, Max Fosh goes around interviewing posh people in London to get their thoughts on the year 2020.
summary: Max Fosh interacts with posh individuals to discuss their experiences and opinions on the year 2020.
payoff: The humor in the video comes from the contrast between the posh individuals' privileged perspectives and the challenges faced by the general population in 2020. Max Fosh's witty interactions with them add to the comedic effect.
